Title: Goods and supplies
Description: This contracting (or planning) process is for physical or electronic goods or supplies.

Title: Works
Description: This contracting (or planning) process is for construction, repair, rehabilitation, demolition, restoration or maintenance of some asset or infrastructure.

Title: Services
Description: This contracting (or planning) process is for professional services of some form, generally contracted for on the basis of measurable outputs or deliverables. When the consultingServices code is also available or in use for data from a particular dataset, the service code must only be used for non-consulting services.

Title: Consulting services
Description: This contracting (or planning) process is for professional services provided on a consultancy basis.
